query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from question AS q1
inner join tag_question AS tq1
on q1.id = tq1.question_id AND q1.view_count >= 100 AND q1.view_count <= 100000
inner join tag AS t1
on t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND t1.name IN ('.net-4.5',
'algorithm',
'heap',
'x86-64')
inner join answer AS a1
on q1.id = a1.question_id
inner join so_user AS u1
on a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND u1.downvotes >= 10 AND u1.downvotes <= 100000
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = tq1.site_id AND s.site_id = q1.site_id AND s.site_id = a1.site_id AND s.site_id = u1.site_id AND s.site_id = t1.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow',
'superuser')
inner join badge AS b
on b.user_id = u1.id AND s.site_id = b.site_id AND b.name IN ('Benefactor',
'Cleanup',
'Copy Editor',
'Documentation User',
'Electorate',
'Epic',
'Fanatic',
'Generalist',
'Lifeboat',
'Publicist',
'Refiner',
'Sportsmanship',
'Steward',
'Strunk & White',
'Tag Editor')
inner join account AS acc
on acc.id = u1.account_id;
